{"tid":609004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港越嚟越垃圾","createTime":"2018-03-28T15:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T19:02:50.000Z","uid":143915,"like":86,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"99621d36d86b709f93925a2eaf0799989d55d9f5","tid":609004,"uid":143915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"市容越嚟越差<br />\n<br />\n啲人越嚟越廢<br />\n<br />\n香港競爭力越嚟越差、國際形象越嚟越差<br />\n<br />\n香港人個朵越嚟越臭、地位越嚟越低<br />\n<br />\n條街越嚟越臭、人越嚟越多、路越嚟越爛<br />\n<br />\n整個城市充斥廢人同庸材 有料嘅晨早去外國發展<br />\n<br />\n啲人越嚟越大陸，一邊瘋狂用/食/買/去/<br />\n玩大陸嘢，一邊自詡比大陸人高級<br />\n<br />\n一日到刻爭取民主，但冇諗過香港民智低到根本無法發揮民主制度的優點<br />\n<br />\n整個城市繼續毫無文化、品味庸俗"},{"pid":"5df305a411218ca5bcbc66f668e5cfbfb621cf2a","tid":609004,"uid":143915,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"香港政府除左賣港乜撚都唔識做<br />\n<br />\n而家所謂嘅高官毫冇領袖風範，只見到一堆淨識聽order做嘢嘅庸材撐場面、完全缺乏領導能力"},{"pid":"99fd3b39db3a1e6e8e42a671bb5225bc2e9236e6","tid":609004,"uid":151490,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce489b71378c744e06ec06143077200d5e951a5c","tid":609004,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e340530d98c5630b5450a629527a17f1be073608","tid":609004,"uid":143915,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"一句講曬，香港係一個未來完全黯淡嘅末落城市，只會越變越衰"},{"pid":"9d35a97db1ac9e1ac70c0a2c90b3b274f8318ae7","tid":609004,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"政府想整死香港有咩計"},{"pid":"5da51daa911ca9ddb80510b2557d488c50d65812","tid":609004,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"有乜野近支會變好？"},{"pid":"a940022ac4d2899ba6b8adee67ac55cbbe348aba","tid":609004,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce489b71378c7